8
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:32,380
but because the

9
00:00:32,380 --> 00:00:33,320
basic framework,

10
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:36,190
the basic structure of all

11
00:00:36,190 --> 00:00:39,060
of physics is based on the

12
00:00:39,060 --> 00:00:40,600
principles of classical mechanics.

13
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:42,660
The conservation of energy,

