evolve in nature is the same set

18
00:00:53,460 --> 00:00:54,080
of rules,

19
00:00:54,080 --> 00:00:56,800
essentially exactly the same set of rules,

20
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:57,080
and the same set of rules,

21
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:57,080
and the same set of rules,

22
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:57,080
and the same set of rules,

23
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:59,210
and the more abstract and the more general

24
00:00:59,210 --> 00:01:01,340
setting than the rules which govern how a

25
00:01:01,340 --> 00:01:02,380
