60
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,860
Let's also imagine a very,

61
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:18,620
very simple set of systems,

62
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:20,680
systems which are so simple

63
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,740
that they only have a handful

64
00:02:22,740 --> 00:02:23,600
