65
00:02:25,180 --> 00:02:26,460
Configurations mean

66
00:02:26,460 --> 00:02:27,040
a number of times,

67
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:28,750
everything we need to know about

68
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:30,440
the system to characterize it completely.

69
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:32,020
So the simplest

70
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:34,030
system I can think of would be

71
00:02:34,030 --> 00:02:36,040
a system that has only two configurations,

72
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:37,260
