214
00:07:07,260 --> 00:07:08,900
What is the evolution of a

215
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:10,540
system under this law of nature?

216
00:07:10,540 --> 00:07:12,120
If you start with heads,

217
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:12,460
it's heads,

218
00:07:12,460 --> 00:07:12,680
tails,

219
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:12,960
heads,

220
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:13,200
tails,

221
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:13,480
heads,

222
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:13,780
tails,

223
00:07:13,780 --> 00:07:13,940
heads,

224
00:07:13,940 --> 00:07:14,200
tails,

225
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:14,860
