226
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:19,120
These are two consistent laws of physics

227
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:22,280
in a world of only two states.

228
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:25,940
Whether we can think of more laws,

229
00:07:25,940 --> 00:07:26,420
yes,

230
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:26,800
we can,

231
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:28,160
but for the moment,

232
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,080
these are two interesting

233
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:29,360
