00:08:02,540 --> 00:08:02,860
5,

261
00:08:02,860 --> 00:08:03,300
and 6.

262
00:08:03,780 --> 00:08:05,170
Which one is 1 and which

263
00:08:05,170 --> 00:08:06,560
one is 6 is not very important,

