274
00:08:23,060 --> 00:08:24,600
You start with a 1 up,

275
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,220
and then it goes to the 2 up,

276
00:08:26,220 --> 00:08:26,700
3 up,

277
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:27,240
and so forth,

278
00:08:27,380 --> 00:08:29,160
