289
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:50,780
3 could go to 2,

290
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:53,500
2 could go to 5,

291
00:08:53,500 --> 00:08:55,960
1,

292
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,460
2,

