tails goes to tails?

1460
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:30,560
Yes.

1461
00:44:30,560 --> 00:44:31,080
That's no good.

1462
00:44:32,140 --> 00:44:32,960
So tails,

1463
00:44:32,960 --> 00:44:33,880
tails goes to tails,

1464
