Bad.

1466
00:44:36,380 --> 00:44:38,200
Not allowable by the laws of physics.

1467
00:44:38,760 --> 00:44:38,960
Yeah.

1468
00:44:39,080 --> 00:44:40,620
You could do an XOR.

1469
00:44:41,240 --> 00:44:42,440
And now tails,

1470
00:44:42,440 --> 00:44:43,100
