Tails,

1474
00:44:46,440 --> 00:44:47,440
tails goes to tails,

1475
00:44:47,440 --> 00:44:47,680
tails?

1476
00:44:48,080 --> 00:44:48,520
Heads,

1477
00:44:48,520 --> 00:44:48,740
tails.

1478
00:44:49,380 --> 00:44:49,820
Wait.

1479
00:44:50,220 --> 00:44:50,660
Tails,

1480
00:44:50,660 --> 00:44:50,780
tails.

1481
